## 3. Items not yet recognised

The entity continues to hold heritage items that have not yet been recognised as assets because their fair value cannot be measured reliably at this date. The existence and nature of those items are disclosed in the heritage register; recognition will be revisited at each reporting date as additional valuation evidence becomes available.

